      "text": "Have a fatigue system to\nencourage moving to next\nday at night time. \nSlows movement/occasional\ntrips/reduced\nvision/increased movement\nlatency (slightly)/makes\nmore noise.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
